hostmot2-firmware (0.8) lucid; urgency=low

  * new firmwares: 5i20/SV12_2X7I48 5i20/SVTP_7I39 ti23/SVTP6_7I39 
  * new upstream vhdl files
  * improved build process (some error exits were not detected)
  * improved documentation for those who would like to build their own
    firmwares

 -- Jeff Epler <jepler@unpythonic.net>  Sun, 19 Dec 2010 10:25:52 -0600

hostmot2-firmware (0.7) hardy; urgency=low

  * New firmware SVST2_4_7i47 for 5i20 (servo and stepper pinout for 7i47
    daughtercard)
  * new firmware TPEN6_6 for 5i20, 5i23, 4i68 and TPEN4_5 for 7i43
    (three-phase motor control, currently compatible with emc2 master only)
  * Fix the hostmot2-firmware-all package so that it actually installs all
    the firmware packages.

 -- Jeff Epler <jepler@unpythonic.net>  Mon, 05 Jul 2010 13:30:48 -0500

hostmot2-firmware (0.6) hardy; urgency=low

  * New xml files describing firmware information in a machine-readable
    fashion.  The exact format should be considered "in flux" until a released
    version of pncconf uses it.
  * Show better information about stepgen and tppwm pins in PIN and xml
    files
  * Fix dependency information that could lead to out-of-date BIT files.

 -- Jeff Epler <jepler@unpythonic.net>  Tue, 27 Apr 2010 07:37:33 -0500

hostmot2-firmware (0.5) hardy; urgency=low

  * New firmwares: i22-*/SVST2_4_7I47, i20/SV12IM_2X7I48
  * Symlinks for compatibility with emc 2.3 firmware locations
  * .PIN files in documentation directory, not in /lib/firmware

 -- Jeff Epler <jepler@unpythonic.net>  Thu, 25 Feb 2010 15:05:03 -0600

